title: Inside the Parker - Nats World Series Madness; Astros Storm Back; Guest: D.C. Anchor Darren Haynes on Washington's Run
itunes:title: Inside the Parker - Nats World Series Madness; Astros Storm Back; Guest: D.C. Anchor Darren Haynes on Washington's Run
description:
This week on Inside the (Rob) Parker, Rob looks at the Nationals continuing their magical postseason run to the World Series after sweeping the Cardinals, the Astros regaining the upper hand in their series against the Yankees, . He also gives the Analytic of The Week, Foul or Fair, and names his Top 3 MLB Teams of the Week.

Guest: Darren Haynes -  D.C. Anchor discusses the buzz in the capital over the Nationals unforgettable postseason ride.
